# API Documentation

## Generate Poster API

The `generatePoster` endpoint creates a HTML poster from markdown content.

**Endpoint:** [src/pages/api/generatePoster.ts](mdc:src/pages/api/generatePoster.ts)

**Method:** POST to `/api/generatePoster`

**Request Body:**
```typescript
{
  markdown: string;       // Markdown content
  header?: string;        // Optional: header text
  footer?: string;        // Optional: footer text
  theme?: 'light' | 'dark'; // Optional: theme
  width?: number;         // Optional: image width
  height?: number;        // Optional: image height
}
```

## Generate Poster Image API

The `generatePosterImage` endpoint creates an image from markdown content.

**Endpoint:** [src/pages/api/generatePosterImage.ts](mdc:src/pages/api/generatePosterImage.ts)

**Method:** POST to `/api/generatePosterImage`

**Request Body:**
```typescript
{
  markdown: string;      // Markdown content
  theme?: string;        // Optional: theme
  width?: number;        // Optional: image width
}
```

